---
By: John Donne
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 10
    Verse: 11
Tags:
  - Adversity
---
Affliction is a treasure, and scarce is any man who hath enough of it. No
man hath affliction enough that is not matured, and ripened by it, and made
fit for God by that affliction.
